c: 3
v: 112
t: "Ihlazo lithiwe wambu phezu kwabo naphi na apho bakhoyo, ngaphandle kwamaxa bephantsi komnqophiso wokhuseleko luka-Allâh, nolwabantu; bona bazibizele ingqumbo ka- Allâh nentshabalalo ibekwe phezu kwabo. Oku kungenxa yokuba abakholwa kwiiVesi zika-Allâh, babulala nabaProfeti ngokungekho lungelweni. Oku kungenxa yokuba basuka bangaMthobeli uAllâh, bagabadela, batsiba imida"